name: NurtiVal
description: An app that helps it's users to get the most of their foods, by displaying how much nurtrients are in the food they are searching for.

name: Note Taker
description: An app that can save and retrieve note data from a JSON.  A User can write and save notes to keep track of anyhing the User wants to take notes of

name: Workout Tracker
description: A web app that a user can view, create, and track daily workouts

name: PWA Budget Tracker
description: A web app that is able to add expenses and deposits to a budget with or without a connection.  When entering transactions offline, the data is stored until an online connection is established then all saved data is uploaded and saved to the app.
